[section#thread.coord.general
    [:en] General
    [:zh_CN] 概述
]

[para]
[:en] Subclause [#thread.coord] describes various concepts related to thread
coordination, and defines the coordination types [`latch] and [`barrier].
[:zh_CN] 子条款 [#thread.coord] 描述多种与线程协作相关的概念，并定义了协作类型
[`latch] 和 [`barrier]。

[:en] These types facilitate concurrent computation performed by a number of
threads.
[:zh_CN] 这些类型有助于由大量线程实施的并发计算。
